Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,LEARN. Cognitive-development analytics for USMC schoolhouses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM use case: Learning Intelligence Dashboard. Are Marines actually\Nlearning?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighteen students. Six assignments. Two hundred forum posts. One\Nquestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Synthetic Moodle export streams in. No data movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A three-stage agent scores every student against the USMC competency\Nrubric, anchored to NAVMC 3500.18 Infantry T&R.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kamiwaza-deployed model drafts the Instructors Competency Brief,\Ncited to NAVMC 3500.18.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-click drill-down: heatmap to student to remediation. Sergeants\NCourse at SNCO Academy is distinct from the Squad Leader Course at …
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Class-level competency map. Top performers. Intervention list.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Every assessment SHA-256 chained. Privacy Act of 1974 and DoDI 1322.35\Ngoverned. SJA, IG, TECOM can replay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Powered by Kamiwaza. Privacy Act 1974 and DoDI 1322.35 governed. IL5\Nready. Deploy in hours.
